These directories contain all of the manual files for the H7 mudlib.

1) A manual file is a file that is too long for the help system, and
   that goes into great detail about some facet of play.

2) The manual file should contain the following file endings.
	a) .wiz for creator only files
	b) .man for general/player files
  Files without endings are assumed to be general viewing files.

3) When a new file is added it must have a UNIQUE name

4) When a new file is added the /fucntion/manuals.c file must be
   updaded. This file contains a mapping of current manual files

